{
  "stem": "20021.5",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Allies are pounding in Normandy and moving towards Paris.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was the Normandy landing succeeded.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At first, it wasn't so sure it will succeed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So Hitler lost the war to everybody except to himself and to Eichmann, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So anyhow, here I am in Bucharest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everything is nice and dandy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And suddenly, I get bounced on the street by two secret agents, and I get arrested.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Some group in the German-- in the Romanian police, wanted to prove, you see, that what we really are, that we are refugees from Nazi concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that they were baloney, but the-- but the papers were saying there, you know, what the Romanian Jews concocted to say about us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they grabbed me to prove the point.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, somebody from within my group must have somehow denounced or said something, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And here I am again taken to the big jail Romania, a real giant building with the police headquarters.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what a bureaucracy there, it is unbelievable the number of policemen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'm constantly being interrogated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the fact of my circumcision becomes an issue.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I try to prove that I'm Jewish, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I have all the proof in the world, including-- And they keep sending me to doctors back and forth.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And because of these scars, the doctors, the bastards, say it's inconclusive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "See?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So next, I'm trying to tell them, look, you give me an exam.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's impossible that somebody will know so much about Jewish prayers and the Talmud and the Torah and all that, that he has suddenly picked this up in a month.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's only in a lifetime of study you can know of that.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
